# Slack incoming webhook for hygiene report (optional)
# Sent on every run — pass or fail — so you always know the org state.
#
# To receive reports as a DM (recommended):
#   1. Go to https://api.slack.com/apps → Create New App → From scratch
#   2. Add feature: Incoming Webhooks → Activate
#   3. "Add New Webhook to Workspace" → choose "Direct Messages > [Your Name]"
#   4. Copy the webhook URL and paste it below
#
# To post to a channel instead, just choose the channel in step 3.
SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL=https://hooks.slack.com/services/YOUR/WEBHOOK/URL

# Optional: override config paths (defaults: src/config/orgs.json, src/config/thresholds.json)
# ORG_CONFIG_PATH=src/config/orgs.json
# THRESHOLDS_PATH=src/config/thresholds.json
